Division of Work

The development of VizPro Max was a collaborative effort with specific roles assigned to leverage individual strengths.

| Team Member | Role | Contribution |
| :---      | :---                        | :---                                                                                                                                           |
| **Arjun** | **Software Lead**           | Architected the hybrid AI system, developed the Python codebase (threading, vision loop, Gemini integration), and handled system optimization. |
| **Nayam** | **Hardware Lead**           | Designed and assembled the robot chassis, managed circuit wiring, integrated sensors/motors, and ensured physical stability.                   |
| **Sayaan** | **Procurement & Logistics** | Sourced components (RPi, camera modules, sensors), managed budget/inventory, and researched component compatibility.                           |
